dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents zoning for Grant County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Grant_Zoning_2018.gdb. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Grant_General_2018' and 'Grant_Shoreland_2018'. [Select data assembled from the County Tax Roll , Certified Survey Maps, Plats of Survey, Public Land Survey System, Municipal CAD files, and other sources. While every effort has been made to ensure reasonable accuracy, the wide range of original data sources throughout Grant County's history, the age and/or accuracy of the data contained herein is not guaranteed.The data provided in this document is for informational purposes only and Grant County assumes no legal responsibility for the information contained in this data. This document is not a legal survey nor is it intended to be used as such.Identifies those parcels restricted by Grant County's Shoreland Zoning Ordinance.]
